        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Hey.\r\nI'm only 95% sure that the filetypes \"javascript.jsx\" and \"typescript.tsx\" are wrong. For the other's I am actually not sure since I'm not using them/know them enough.\r\n\r\nIf you say that they need to stay I'll add them back in.",
