        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> filetypes \"javascript.jsx\" and \"typescript.tsx\"\r\n\r\nwe decided to remove those in https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/pull/4253 and https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/pull/4299 so those can be dropped.\r\n\r\nhbs and mdx look like file extensions so are probably wrong.\r\n\r\nso only `handlebars` should stay",
